== Overview ==
The standard multi-launch rocket pack, the MR100 can inflict serious damage to multiple targets on the battlefield.

== Where to Acquire ==
The MR100 Rocket Pack can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
